  "title": "Improving income and food supply in the Sahel – On-farm testing of sorghum and pearl millet technologies: summary proceedings of the Stakeholders’ Workshop to Plan and Implement the IFAD Project, ICRISAT, Sadoré, Niger, 24-26 Feb 1999",
